k_range = range(1, 31)
values = []
for k in k_range:
    knn = KNeighborsRegressor(n_neighbors=k)
    knn.fit(x_train, y_train)
    y_pred = knn.predict(x_test)
    values.append(knn.score(x_test, y_test))
print(values)
